name: Jurajski Sen
overview: Jurajski Sen is a platform game. The story begins during the session of the hit movie "Jurassic Dream". After returning home, the main character plays computer game for a while and goes to sleep. While dreaming he is transferred in a prehistoric times where he must survive and find a talisman - the key to return home. Using the club and jumping ability with a help of power ups, such as extra life or temporary immortality the player must go through numerous enemies (caveman's, bouncing heads, various types of dinosaurs) and obstacles (fire camp, falling stones, sharp spikes and deadly skulls) scattered throughout the five levels of the game.
